<TEXT>
   Kitty Dukakis sent a get-well telegram to first
lady Barbara Bush, who underwent radioactive thyroid treatment.
   ``Best wishes for a speedy recovery,'' the wife of former
Democratic presidential nominee Michael S. Dukakis wrote Mrs. Bush.
   A spokeswoman for the Massachusetts governor said Mrs. Dukakis
