<FIRST>r a AM-StinkyGym     04-13 0317</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Stinky Gym,0326</SECOND>
<HEAD>Students Protest Mississippi School's Aroma</HEAD>
<DATELINE>JACKSON, Miss. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Nobody expects a high school gym to smell
like a rose garden, but the locker room in one Jackson school is so
wilting it drove some students to picket.
   ``Cure That Smell,'' one student's sign read. Another
proclaimed: ``Brinkley Gym Stinks _ We Need Help Now, Not Later.''
   The six Brinkley Junior High students who picketed Wednesday
morning were ordered by Assistant Principal Charles Borden to
either return to class, go home or face police, said 15-year-old
Alisha Smith, a ninth-grader.
   ``We feel like what we are doing is right,'' Smith said as the
group headed away from the school.
   While students are worried about scents, school administrators
are holding their breath over the dollars they may have to spend to
deodorize the school.
   They say the area's troublesome Yazoo clay is shifting the
foundation and causing sewer pipes to emit foul odors.
   ``The sewage gas is being trapped and is coming back into some
of the drains _ particularly in the girl's dressing room area of
the gym and, to some extent, some of the science labs,'' said
Reuben Dilworth, assistant superintendent for Jackson's junior high
schools.
   Engineers hired by the school district are examining the pipes
and will make recommendations, Dilworth said. Crews also are
checking to see if the foundation is damaged, and the state
Department of Health said it is testing water samples from the
campus as a precaution.
   Principal Charles Tillman said female students aren't being
asked to don gym uniforms because of conditions in their locker
room.
   The aroma has been noticeable for weeks, the students said, but
became unbearable Wednesday.
   ``You can walk down the hall and in the cafeteria, and when you
go to biology, nothing but gnats fly up your nose when you sniff,''
said Patricia Stubbs, a ninth-grader who joined the student picket
line.
</TEXT>
