<FIRST>u f PM-WallStreetNoon CORRECTION   04-13 0304</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Wall Street Noon, CORRECTION,0318</SECOND>
<UNK>Eds: Fixes Typo in Coke stock price 8th graf</UNK>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market drifted lower today as traders
warily awaited the latest reading on inflation.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials dropped 10.08 to
2,309.57 by noontime on Wall Street.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by about 7 to 4 in nationwide trading
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 457 up, 788 down and
550 unchanged.
